<!-- Page 20: Fertilization -->
<div class="page" id="page21" style="display: none;">
    <h1>‚ûî Fertilization</h1>
    <p><strong>Fertilization</strong> is the process where a sperm cell fuses with an egg cell. This fusion of the <strong>two haploid</strong> gametes creates a <strong>diploid zygote</strong>, which has a complete set of chromosomes. The <strong>zygote</strong> will undergo mitosis in order to develop into a new individual.</p>

    <div class="button-container">
        <button onclick="gameOver()">Game Over</button>
    </div>
    
